    <t id="412">Lacks required seminars for this training. [Missing: Basic x%1, 1-Star x%2, 2-Star x%3, 3-Star x%4]</t>
    <t id="413">Lacks required seminars for this training. [Missing: Basic x%1, 1-Star x%2, 2-Star x%3, 3-Star x%4, 4-Star x%5]</t>
    <t id="414">Not enough unassigned crew; captains will be appointed to some ships only.</t>
